Metavariable P:Statement
Metavariable Q:Statement

Rule (NegationIntroductionAlternativeForm)
  Premise
    P ⇒ (Q ∧ ¬Q)
  Conclusion
    ¬P
  Proof
    P ⇒ Q by ConjunctionLeftEliminationWithImplication
    P ⇒ ¬Q by ConjunctionRightEliminationWithImplication
  Therefore
    ¬P by NegationIntroduction
